# Design System "Claude-style" — Reglas visuales

## Tokens CSS — NUNCA hardcodear colores

```tsx
// ❌ MAL
style={{ backgroundColor: "#FAF9F5", border: "1px solid #e8e8e8" }}
className="bg-white border-gray-200"

// ✅ BIEN
className="bg-bg"
style={{ border: "0.5px solid var(--border)" }}
```

## Border system — SIEMPRE 0.5px inline, nunca Tailwind `border-border`

```tsx
// ❌ MAL — genera 1px
className="border border-border"
className="border-b border-border"

// ✅ BIEN — 0.5px
style={{ border: "0.5px solid var(--border)" }}
style={{ borderBottom: "0.5px solid var(--border)" }}
style={{ borderTop: "0.5px solid var(--border)" }}
```

## Tokens de texto disponibles
- `text-fg` — primario (#141413)
- `text-fg-muted` — secundario (#3D3D3A)  
- `text-fg-subtle` — terciario (#73726C)

## Botón primario = OSCURO
```tsx
// Default variant ya es dark (#141413) via --primary
<Button variant="default">Acción</Button>  // ✅ oscuro
<Button variant="accent">Acción</Button>   // azul #0066cc
```

## Recharts contentStyle — 0.5px
```tsx
contentStyle={{ background: "var(--surface)", border: "0.5px solid var(--border)", borderRadius: "8px" }}
```
